OL,4,Cpassport guidance from website
OL,6,FGuernsey's government has removed
OL,7,Fincorrect guidance on European travel
OL,8,Frules from its official website after
OL,9,Fbeing alerted to the error by a travel
OL,10,Fjournalist.
OL,12,FSimon Calder says the passport advice
OL,13,Fwas "completely wrong" and he is
OL,14,Fcalling on officials and companies to
OL,15,Fcheck their sources as he argues it
OL,16,F"simply shouldn't be happening".
