OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Channel, Simon adds:
OL,7,F"The Government of Guernsey was saying
OL,8,Fwhat a lot of the travel industry, and
OL,9,Findeed for a time even the Foreign
OL,10,FOffice in London was saying,
OL,11,Fcompletely wrongly.
OL,13,F"Which is, 'Oh you're going to the
OL,14,FEuropean Union, your passport isn't
OL,15,Fvalid after nine years and nine
OL,16,Fmonths'.
OL,18,F"That is the case for some, but for an
OL,19,Fawful lot of people that's certainly
OL,20,Fnot the case."
