OL,6,FIn a report for The Independent, Simon
OL,7,Fexplains that four years on from post-
OL,8,FBrexit rule changes, Guernsey's
OL,9,Fgovernment was incorrectly stating
OL,10,Fthat a British passport is "valid for
OL,11,Ftravel into Schengen countries for
OL,12,Fnine years and nine months from its
OL,13,Foriginal issue date".
