OL,6,FInstead, since the UK left the
OL,7,FEuropean Union, travellers with a
OL,8,FBritish passport must ensure it was
OL,9,Fissued less than ten years before the
OL,10,Fday they arrive in a Schengen Area
OL,11,Fcountry and they also need at least
OL,12,Fthree months remaining on the document
OL,13,Fon the day they are due to leave.
OL,15,FSimon Calder's two tests to check if a
OL,16,FBritish passport is valid for travel
OL,17,Fto the European Union:
OL,19,FThe Schengen Area covers 29 member
OL,20,Fstates including France, Germany and
OL,21,FSpain.
