OL,6,FHowever, there has been widespread
OL,7,Fconfusion over the post-Brexit rules.
OL,9,FSimon says: "I saw that this was
OL,10,Fhappening in Guernsey and got on to
OL,11,Ftheir government and to their credit,
OL,12,Fthey took the guidance down.
OL,14,F"Guernsey's government did say, 'We're
OL,15,Fgetting lots of stories of people
OL,16,Fbeing turned away and that's what we
OL,17,Fwant to avoid' and so I said, 'Yes I
OL,18,Fcan understand that but it is having
OL,19,Fthe wrong information, online at an
OL,20,Fofficial source, which is helping to
OL,21,Ffuel this complete misunderstanding'."
