OL,4,Cpassport guidance from website
OL,6,FIn response to Simon's report,
OL,7,FGuernsey Customs and Immigration
OL,8,FService has admitted its error,
OL,9,Fadding: "While certain rules and areas
OL,10,Fdo allow passports to be used for over
OL,11,Ften years, as you have correctly
OL,12,Fpointed out, many members of our
OL,13,Fcommunity have previously encountered
OL,14,Fissues with airlines at check-ins
OL,15,Fwhere those airlines do not recognise
OL,16,Fthis is the case and have not been
OL,17,Fallowed on to their flight.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
