OL,6,F"Our advice, therefore, is aimed to
OL,7,Fhelp the community ensure they do not
OL,8,Fencounter these issues. Going
OL,9,Fforwards, we will ensure our websites
OL,10,Fsimply refer people to the FCDO
OL,11,F(Foreign, Commonwealth and Development
OL,12,FOffice) and EU websites."
